{"tid":854293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"娛圈「自首時間表」出爐　年底死線","createTime":"2018-10-09T09:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T10:52:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ea08ff34eddd36d4df502aa8b1c03f1af94675","tid":854293,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181009/20517782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517782&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=04146c77\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181009%2F20517782&h=5ca71d4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181009/20517782</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年10月09日 <br />\n<br />\n娛圈「自首時間表」出爐　年底死線<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181009/large/09cx01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181009%2Flarge%2F09cx01p.jpg&h=076aed25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n范冰冰案再有新進展，昨日有五名涉案官員受罰。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方昨除了公佈對相關稅務官員作行政處分外，稅務總局亦訂出至明年7月底、針對影視界逃稅的「自首」時間表，今年底前主動補交稅款者可毋須受罰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181009/large/a1502a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181009%2Flarge%2Fa1502a.gif&h=e61c2273&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n補交稅免罰<br />\n<br />\n根據公告，國稅總局要求各地稅務機關按照分步實施的原則，展開規範影視行業稅收工作。有關工作分為三階段，自周三（10日）起，稅務機關將通知演藝公司、藝員等，對2016年後的申報納稅情況「自查自糾」，在年底前補交稅款便可免去處罰。<br />\n<br />\n明年1月至2月，當局將會有針對性地督促納稅人繳款，經提醒後繳款者可從輕處罰。至於死不悔改的逃稅者，稅務部門將在明年3月至6月展開重點檢查，並依法嚴肅處理。在明年7月底前，當局目標建立影視界稅收管理長效機制，同時要求打擊稅務部門和官員的違法違紀問題，對出現大範圍偷逃稅行為而未履職者要嚴肅查處。<br />\n<br />\n對於范冰冰巨額逃稅卻免入獄，民間仍然有很大爭議。「自首」時間表與官員懲處同日公佈，官方在逃稅風波上的處理用意相當明顯。評論認為，當局只為讓其他逃稅影星自動「嘔返筆錢」，「坐監的話又點會叫到人『回水』？」<br />\n<br />\n另亦有分析指，影視行業涉及個人、利益集團眾多，難以逐一篩查，在限期前補交稅款免罰款，可以用最低成本、最大程度彌補損失。<br />\n<br />\n新華社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n當局輕罰圖息民憤　范冰冰案芝麻官記過<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n內地新盤狂劈價　業主怒砸售樓處"},{"pid":"eb3871983e1166dbe5adef328d468b72f6f41271","tid":854293,"uid":26329,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:22:15.000Z","msg":"香港班愛國藝人係時候愛國啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2d9889482a7dfb7de611bb1d86dd0a4419caee","tid":854293,"uid":152476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:23:52.000Z","msg":"香港個班呢"},{"pid":"337a19f5c9865dd62095e387dda05f11d261ac6a","tid":854293,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:30:15.000Z","msg":"香港藝人係時候報答國家"},{"pid":"89cba5e1813f089a1af80de961d2731019e303f7","tid":854293,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"離開支那，咪搞得掂囉"},{"pid":"40163816dab746e97a3ed6a555cf5320f244e3bc","tid":854293,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:32:06.000Z","msg":"成蟲咁撚有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c24701ff5f8870802f385ff8d54a0810bd069f","tid":854293,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:33:50.000Z","msg":"咁搞法會唔會有人申請政治庇護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9188c446dd582b6dfff65c416e2609b162d95076","tid":854293,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:34:40.000Z","msg":"年底<br />\n而家都10月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"488eb45d21d87380897f7e0e6da030011c65cc76","tid":854293,"uid":87723,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"蝗袓藍<br />\n瘋蝗gem<br />\n陳大春